WEBVTT

00:05.122 --> 00:11.091
My name is Ryan Etheridge and you are listening to our podcast series focused around the gospel of Christ according to Matthew.

00:11.752 --> 00:20.566
Today's date is Friday, February 27th and our scripture focus is going to be on Matthew chapter 21 verse 23 through 46.

00:22.069 --> 00:32.946
And so in the first few verses here of our passage, verse 23 through 27, we see that Jesus' authority is

00:33.090 --> 00:33.571
challenge.

00:33.591 --> 00:35.633
So he's come into Jerusalem at that point.

00:35.913 --> 00:44.164
He's come to take part of the Passover celebration, which as we know will eventually lead up to his arrest and ultimately crucifixion.

00:44.564 --> 00:48.048
But in this moment, he's already come into the city.

00:48.149 --> 00:51.773
They've done the whole Palm Sunday thing, Hosanna in the highest.

